   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="address"><address><addrLine><pb facs="1907_AS_RBH_1_00034"/><hi rend="pre-print"><hi rend="capitals"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb47570">Hôtel <c rendition="#kaufmannsund"/>
                           Pension Bavaria</rs><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><rs ref="#pmb11483" type="place">Meran-Obermais</rs></hi></hi></addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="pre-print"><hi rend="capitals">Hôtel <c rendition="#kaufmannsund"/> Pension <rs ref="#pmb723" type="place">Wildbad Waldbrunn</rs>, <rs type="place" ref="#pmb724">Pustertal</rs></hi></hi></addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="pre-print"><hi rend="capitals">Besitzer: <rs ref="#pmb47572" type="person">Jos. Böhm</rs></hi></hi></addrLine></address><address><addrLine><hi rend="latintype">Herrn Dr. Rich</hi></addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="latintype">Beer-Hofmann</hi></addrLine><addrLine><rs type="place" ref="#pmb909"><hi rend="latintype">Velden</hi></rs></addrLine><addrLine><rs type="place" ref="#pmb430"><hi rend="latintype">am Wörthersee</hi></rs></addrLine><addrLine><rs ref="#pmb40118" type="place"><hi rend="latintype">Etabl. Wahliss</hi></rs></addrLine></address></div>
         <div type="writingSession" n="1"><opener><dateline rend="right"><pb facs="1907_AS_RBH_1_00036"/><rs ref="#pmb723" type="place"><hi rend="latintype">Welsb.-Waldbr.</hi></rs><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><date when="1907-08-25">25. 8 907</date></dateline><salute rend="inline">lieber Richard,</salute></opener><p>wir fahren morgen <date>26.</date> von hier fort. (<rs ref="#pmb12692" type="person">Heini</rs> direct nach <rs ref="#pmb50" type="place">Wien</rs>.) <rs ref="#pmb2173" type="person">Olga</rs> u ich (höch<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>twahr<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>cheinlich) <rs ref="#pmb40343" type="place">Waidbruck</rs>, übernachten. Da<c rendition="#gemination-n">nn</c> durchs <rs ref="#pmb40350" type="place">Grödner
                  Thal</rs>, <rs ref="#pmb40346" type="place">Grödnerjoch</rs>, <hi rend="latintype"><rs ref="#pmb40366" type="place">Corvara</rs> – <rs ref="#pmb40354" type="place">Arabba</rs></hi> – <rs ref="#pmb40369" type="place">Pordoj</rs>, – <rs ref="#pmb40362" type="place">Vigo</rs> – <rs ref="#pmb40371" type="place"><hi rend="latintype">Karer</hi><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ee</rs> – <rs ref="#pmb40260" type="place"><hi rend="latintype">Bozen</hi></rs>. Manches zu Fu<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>s, manches zu Wagen; Modificationen nicht ausge<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>chlo<c rendition="#langesS">s</c><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>en.
               Höch<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>twahr<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>cheinlich Sam<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>tag oder So<c rendition="#gemination-n">nn</c>tag<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ind wir in <rs ref="#pmb40260" type="place">Bozen</rs>, wollen aber <add place="above">von</add>
               dort direct nach <rs ref="#pmb43520" type="place">Meran</rs> weiter, um dort, in <pb facs="1907_AS_RBH_1_00037"/>dem uns lebhaft empfohlenen parkumgebenen <rs ref="#pmb41086" type="place"><hi rend="latintype">Palasthotel</hi></rs> etwa 8 Tage zu bleiben. Da<c rendition="#gemination-n">nn</c> wohl –(vielleicht mit
               Aufenthalt in <rs ref="#pmb40260" type="place"><hi rend="latintype">Bozen</hi></rs> (<rs ref="#pmb41083" type="place"><hi rend="latintype">Mendel</hi></rs>) – <rs ref="#pmb867" type="place">I<c rendition="#gemination-n">nn</c>sbruck</rs>
                  (<anchor type="commentary" xml:id="K_L01702-1"/><rs type="place" ref="#pmb41093" subtype="implied"><rs ref="#pmb5626" type="person"><hi rend="latintype">Theoderich</hi></rs></rs><note type="commentary" corresp="K_L01702-1">Die Statue <rs ref="#pmb5626" type="person">Theoderichs des Großen</rs> von <rs ref="#pmb41097" type="person">Peter Vischer</rs> (dem Älteren) in der <rs ref="#pmb41093" type="place">Innsbrucker Hofkirche</rs> spielt in <rs ref="#pmb2121" type="person">Schnitzlers</rs> Erzählung <rs ref="#pmb33776" type="work">Dämmerseele</rs>
                  eine zentrale Rolle.</note>) – <rs ref="#pmb30" type="place">Salzburg</rs> (<rs ref="#pmb30" type="place">Salzburg</rs>)–) nach <rs ref="#pmb50" type="place">Wien</rs>. –</p><p>Ein Telegra<c rendition="#gemination-m">mm</c><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><subst><del rend="strikethrough"><date>Freitag</date></del><add place="above"><date>Do<c rendition="#gemination-n">nn</c>er<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>tag</date></add></subst><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><hi rend="latintype"><rs ref="#pmb40371" type="place">Karersee</rs> post rest</hi> hat Chance uns zu
               erreichen. Vielleicht ent<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>chließen Sie<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ich auch zu <rs ref="#pmb43520" type="place">Meran</rs>. <rs ref="#pmb39975" type="place">Gardasee</rs> werden wir diesmal
                  (diesmal<c rendition="#dots" n="3"/>!) wohl nicht mitnehmen. In dem <rs ref="#pmb40371" type="place"><hi rend="latintype">Karer</hi><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ee</rs>telegr. vermerken Sie vielleicht, we<c rendition="#gemination-n">nn</c>s geht, wo Sie <date>Sam<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>tag</date><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><pb facs="1907_AS_RBH_1_00037"/>u <date>So<c rendition="#gemination-n">nn</c>tag</date><hi rend="latintype">telegr.</hi> zu erreichen<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ind. –</p><p><rs ref="#pmb11485" type="person"><hi rend="latintype">Goldmann</hi></rs> i<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>t mit <rs type="person" ref="#pmb17163" subtype="implied">Mutter</rs> in <rs ref="#pmb40474" type="place"><hi rend="latintype">Gossensass</hi></rs> verblieben, wie er mir auf mündl Weg ausrichten lie<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>s. –</p><p>Leben Sie wohl,<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>eien Sie Alle gegrüßt und la<c rendition="#langesS">s</c><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>en Sie mich hoffen, d<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>s wir einander
               bald wieder<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ehen.</p><closer>Herzlich<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>t Ihr<lb/><signed>A.</signed></closer></div>
      </body>
